<p>In fact, when I try to duplicate this feature with my own code, I fail:</p>

<pre><code>struct MyValueTuple&lt;A, B&gt;
{
    public A Item1;
    public B Item2;

    public MyValueTuple(A item1, B item2)
    {
        Item1 = item1;
        Item2 = item2;
